        <div class="cap-row-head">
          <span class="cap-num">01</span>
          <h3>Risk Intelligence & Financial Signals</h3>
          <span class="arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <p>Continuous surveillance across positions, portfolios, and market conditions. Anomaly detection, threshold alerting, operator-in-loop review — built for institutions that cannot afford surprises.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Risk Radar</span><span class="tag">Sentiment Engine</span>
          <span class="tag">Market Feeds</span><span class="tag">Alpaca</span><span class="tag">Bloomberg</span>
